&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; Lord Perseus opened the door to the lower level of the base, and water
&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; poured into the room. He motioned for everyone to follow.
&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; &quot;It looks like that ship we saw crash landed in the ocean...&quot; he said
&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; mater of factly. &quot;Look at this place.&quot;
&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; What had once been their base was now a slab of concrete and metal
&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; with the ocasional structural support poking up from the foundation.
&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; The city, in just as bad of shape, was errily flat with a large number
&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; of buildings simply washed away.
&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; &quot;Looks like we need a new base.&quot; said Guardia steping quietly behind
&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; Lord Perseus, sloshing water with each step.
&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; &quot;This base was build from an old hanger, it wasnt intended to take
&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; that kind of punishment. We could rebuild here, or we could find a
&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; better location. First we need to make sure the townsfolk are ok;
&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; I&#39;ll try to signal Salveo&#39;s team, we&#39;re going to need that shuttle.&quot;
&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; Meanwhile...
&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; Celeron lept up from his chair to stair at some strange radar
&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; readings. An entire sector on the map had temporarily darkened, then
&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; went clear again. The mass that represnted Atlantis didnt look right.
&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; He knew it had changed in the last minion attack; but this didnt even
&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; look like the same city anymore.
&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; &quot;Blast... looks like we need to go see what&#39;s going on.&quot; said Celeron
&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; to himself. &quot;Predecons! Report!&quot;
&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; OOC: This would be the Iron Skull predecon base,
&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; Meanwhile...
&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; Salveo walked into the room where Lord Elder was working.
&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; &quot;Atlantis was just devastated by a tidal wave. We&#39;re going to have to
&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; go back there and assist them.; our base was destroyed.&quot;
